{"tid":1660241,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果我嗌光復香港，佢唔再係我身邊應時代革命","createTime":"2019-10-17T11:48:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T12:15:55.000Z","uid":303778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"12ffe5ee5f4fcacb0794bdb615882cf11ec3ed23","tid":1660241,"uid":303778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T11:48:45.000Z","msg":"香港人發夢左4個月，我地都出左好多次黎。有人話生於亂世，仲慶幸有人係隔離陪你一齊行過。係啊，大家都各自同朋友出去發夢，好彩我身邊仲有個同樣政見，可以理性討論既人同我一齊行出去，為香港既未來發聲。<br />\n<br />\n但係有日我想行出去既時候，搵唔到呢個人，冇人再帶住我避催淚彈，同我一齊嗌五大訴求，話俾我知，如果我俾黑警拉左，佢實會打7佢&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n我再堅持唔到啦，等唔到出去煲底除低gear同大家相認&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，"},{"pid":"b2fd71726dd98810e3ca929fb963ea9cd00638df","tid":1660241,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T11:49:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eD1QUeo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeD1QUeo.jpg&h=564aedde&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"45e0a03e0c2c737d6c0606bea0e55c63e9cf240f","tid":1660241,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T11:51:44.000Z","msg":"終結兒登五毛風向，勿再屌勇武同南亞手足<br />\n［星期日結論］［逆風而行］遊行有批帶gear，守重慶。冇批開花賀佢老母<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1660232\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1660232</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8480e7983331dfb783b4ba9eb6b56b23e45d5326","tid":1660241,"uid":303304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T11:52:07.000Z","msg":"手足，咪做傻事"},{"pid":"91356696a019f02db66fcb1392005317fce5bb08","tid":1660241,"uid":277991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T11:53:32.000Z","msg":"唔好做傻事"},{"pid":"5f21db064988c84849cbfa26cb85494a113f65b3","tid":1660241,"uid":41199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T11:57:58.000Z","msg":"我地需要你/妳 你唔應該受懲罰，請更加唔好懲罰自己"},{"pid":"b3c7756f7d0ded59fbb90e901f2ee23f6f3e3151","tid":1660241,"uid":303778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"